name: Workeroffloading
tagline: A Framework for Offloading webworker from browser to server
body:
### Worker offloading

A Framework for Offloading webworker from browser to server.
offloading Javascript without any change.

### About

##### Client

 replace the Worker API of browser  

##### Server

run worker in server on node

##### Connection

using socket post message

### Authors and Contributors
With the help of nkgongxl (@nkgongxl) New Future (@NewFuture), Xu Haocong (@haocong), and Zhao Wenjian (@zhaowenjian) founded GitHub.
Contributors Liu Chengcheng.
